{"tid":1342052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候反抗啦 醒未啊香港人","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T17:14:01.000Z","uid":158899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5e1927f57827b7d9ec92f6fd1f7eacf4529bdd59","tid":1342052,"uid":158899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:12:25.000Z","msg":"一個月有多既遊行、集會、沖擊、靜坐、絕食<br />\n但係我哋換得返嚟嘅警察開槍布袋彈、煙霧彈、催淚彈、警棍、獅子王<br />\n21號晚上元朗發生白色衫人士圍毆市民男女老少、記者、議員、破壞公物<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇敢啲啦香港人真係想同佢哋打過嘅得一兩個 個個都走晒後退咁前面果一兩個呢俾人打到死？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9a54b098342045e3ae4d684b7a91a753228f6e","tid":1342052,"uid":158899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:14:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">做野未啊香港政府</span></span>"}]}